ADDITIONAL INFORMATION:

This pipeline wraps and utilizes SPINGO (SPecies level IdentificatioN 
of metaGenOmic amplicons), which is also licensed under GPL-3.0.

SPINGO Copyright (C) 2014 Department of Microbiology, University College Cork

When using this pipeline, please cite the original SPINGO publication:

Allard G, Ryan FJ, Jeffery IB, Claesson MJ. SPINGO: a rapid species-classifier 
for microbial amplicon sequences. BMC Bioinformatics. 2015 Oct 8;16(1):324. 
doi: 10.1186/s12859-015-0747-1. PubMed PMID: 26450747; PubMed Central PMCID: 
PMC4599320.

